# game/Scenes/Jamie/JamieTV/jamietv1.rpy:14
translate portuguese jamietv1_917dd9af:

    # "I follow Jamie into the living room and sit down on the couch next to her."
    "Sigo a Jamie até à sala de estar e sento-me no sofá ao lado dela."

# game/Scenes/Jamie/JamieTV/jamietv1.rpy:15
translate portuguese jamietv1_48789a88:

    # "The show starts up pretty soon after we sit down, and I try to watch while Jamie talks through every scene, explaining who all the characters are."
    "O programa começa pouco depois de nos sentarmos, e eu tento ver enquanto a Jamie comenta cada cena, explicando quem são todas as personagens."

# game/Scenes/Jamie/JamieTV/jamietv1.rpy:18
translate portuguese jamietv1_f26b00c3:

    # "Over time, she moves closer to me so she doesn't have to speak as loudly for me to hear her during the show."
    "Com o tempo, ela aproxima-se de mim para não ter de falar tão alto para que eu a ouça durante o programa."

# game/Scenes/Jamie/JamieTV/jamietv1.rpy:19
translate portuguese jamietv1_7488a7ce:

    # gnd "See Cyndi is the older sister and she was married to Winston, but they got divorced and now she's dating Elroy."
    gnd "Vês, a Cyndi é a irmã mais velha e era casada com o Winston, mas divorciaram-se e agora ela namora com o Elroy."

# game/Scenes/Jamie/JamieTV/jamietv1.rpy:20
translate portuguese jamietv1_e33871b4:

    # gnd "The younger sister is Carolyn..."
    gnd "A irmã mais nova é a Carolyn..."

# game/Scenes/Jamie/JamieTV/jamietv1.rpy:21
translate portuguese jamietv1_76d94bb8:

    # "She goes on like this for a while, giving me the recap of the last eight seasons of this show that I don't care about in the slightest."
    "Ela continua assim por um tempo, a fazer-me um resumo das últimas oito temporadas desta série que não me interessa nem um pouco."

# game/Scenes/Jamie/JamieTV/jamietv1.rpy:22
translate portuguese jamietv1_2078b7b8:

    # "I just watch her, my eyes roaming over every inch of her body, nodding along as her mouth moved, thinking about how it would feel to kiss those lips."
    "Limito-me a observá-la, com os olhos a percorrerem cada centímetro do seu corpo, acenando com a cabeça enquanto a boca dela se move, a pensar em como seria beijar aqueles lábios."

# game/Scenes/Jamie/JamieTV/jamietv1.rpy:23
translate portuguese jamietv1_e50f84f6:

    # "I have a hard time taking my eyes away from her to watch the screen."
    "Tenho dificuldade em tirar os olhos dela para olhar para o ecrã."

# game/Scenes/Jamie/JamieTV/jamietv1.rpy:24
translate portuguese jamietv1_dec3d4b8:

    # "I think about putting my arm around her. I want to hold her close, to feel her warmth against me."
    "Penso em passar o braço à volta dela. Quero abraçá-la com força, sentir o seu calor contra mim."

# game/Scenes/Jamie/JamieTV/jamietv1.rpy:25
translate portuguese jamietv1_1ebc9500:

    # "But I'm afraid of pushing too far, too fast, too soon after finally fixing our relationship."
    "Mas tenho medo de ir longe demais, rápido demais, cedo demais, depois de finalmente termos consertado a nossa relação."

# game/Scenes/Jamie/JamieTV/jamietv1.rpy:27
translate portuguese jamietv1_4aa5af9b:

    # "When the show ends and the sappy music starts up while the credits roll, she looks up at me and I look into her eyes."
    "Quando a série termina e a música sentimental começa enquanto os créditos rolam, ela olha para mim e eu olho nos seus olhos."

# game/Scenes/Jamie/JamieTV/jamietv1.rpy:28
translate portuguese jamietv1_0e8a8301:

    # "A moment passes between us. We don't say anything, but I can see that she likes me just as much as I like her."
    "Um momento passa entre nós. Não dizemos nada, mas consigo ver que ela gosta de mim tanto quanto eu gosto dela."

# game/Scenes/Jamie/JamieTV/jamietv1.rpy:29
translate portuguese jamietv1_d17d6173:

    # "I can see that she wants me to kiss her."
    "Consigo ver que ela quer que eu a beije."

# game/Scenes/Jamie/JamieTV/jamietv1.rpy:31
translate portuguese jamietv1_c26dfc22:

    # "I lean in, our lips only millimeters away."
    "Inclino-me, com os nossos lábios a apenas milímetros de distância."

# game/Scenes/Jamie/JamieTV/jamietv1.rpy:32
translate portuguese jamietv1_574266fe:

    # "Then the front door opens and Jamie's dad walks in."
    "Então a porta da frente abre-se e o pai da Jamie entra."

# game/Scenes/Jamie/JamieTV/jamietv1.rpy:35
translate portuguese jamietv1_9ebb9cac:

    # "He looks directly at me, his face immediately dropping into a bulldog-like scowl."
    "Ele olha diretamente para mim, o rosto assumindo imediatamente uma expressão carrancuda, tipo bulldog."

# game/Scenes/Jamie/JamieTV/jamietv1.rpy:38
translate portuguese jamietv1_ceb35d85:

    # "Jamie pulls away from me quickly and rushes over to him."
    "A Jamie afasta-se de mim rapidamente e corre para ele."

# game/Scenes/Jamie/JamieTV/jamietv1.rpy:39
translate portuguese jamietv1_eda53ec0:

    # gnd "Hi, Daddy. I made lasagna for dinner. There's some wrapped in foil in the fridge for you to warm up."
    gnd "Olá, papá. Fiz lasanha para o jantar. Há um pouco embrulhada em papel de alumínio no frigorífico para aqueceres."

# game/Scenes/Jamie/JamieTV/jamietv1.rpy:41
translate portuguese jamietv1_72f1a03e:

    # jd "Sounds great, honey."
    jd "Parece ótimo, querida."

# game/Scenes/Jamie/JamieTV/jamietv1.rpy:45
translate portuguese jamietv1_f2a9fe7e:

    # "He walks up to her and wraps her in a hug."
    "Ele aproxima-se dela e envolve-a num abraço."

# game/Scenes/Jamie/JamieTV/jamietv1.rpy:46
translate portuguese jamietv1_dee4a8d0:

    # jd "It's late. Send him home."
    jd "Já é tarde. Manda-o para casa."

# game/Scenes/Jamie/JamieTV/jamietv1.rpy:47
translate portuguese jamietv1_1976ecec:

    # "With that, he walks past me into the kitchen without ever laying eyes on me."
    "Dito isto, ele passa por mim e entra na cozinha sem sequer me olhar."

# game/Scenes/Jamie/JamieTV/jamietv1.rpy:51
translate portuguese jamietv1_d4db5419:

    # pc "I guess it is late. I should get out of here."
    pc "Acho que é tarde. Devo ir-me embora."

# game/Scenes/Jamie/JamieTV/jamietv1.rpy:53
translate portuguese jamietv1_d41d8cd9:

    # voice "voices/jamie_009b.mp3"
    voice "voices/jamie_009b.mp3"

# game/Scenes/Jamie/JamieTV/jamietv1.rpy:54
translate portuguese jamietv1_c2f845d0:

    # gnd "I'm sorry. I'm trying with him. I told him that you've changed, but he doesn't want to hear it."
    gnd "Desculpa. Estou a tentar com ele. Disse-lhe que mudaste, mas ele não quer ouvir."

# game/Scenes/Jamie/JamieTV/jamietv1.rpy:55
translate portuguese jamietv1_ce223137:

    # pc "It's okay. I understand."
    pc "Não faz mal. Eu compreendo."

# game/Scenes/Jamie/JamieTV/jamietv1.rpy:57
translate portuguese jamietv1_6c7c60bd:

    # gnd "I had fun watching the show with you though. Maybe we can do it again sometime?"
    gnd "Mas diverti-me a ver o programa contigo. Talvez possamos repetir isso um dia destes?"

# game/Scenes/Jamie/JamieTV/jamietv1.rpy:58
translate portuguese jamietv1_0691c9a4:

    # pc "I'd love to."
    pc "Adoraria."

# game/Scenes/Jamie/JamieTV/jamietv1.rpy:59
translate portuguese jamietv1_6260e3d8:

    # "I don't care anything about the show, but I definitely want to spend some more time alone with her."
    "Não me interessa nada o programa, mas quero definitivamente passar mais algum tempo a sós com ela."

# game/Scenes/Jamie/JamieTV/jamietv1.rpy:60
translate portuguese jamietv1_6ce29231:

    # "It had felt like a spark had ignited between us in that moment where we almost kissed, but now it's gone. I want to feel that again."
    "Parecia que tinha surgido uma faísca entre nós naquele momento em que quase nos beijámos, mas agora desapareceu. Quero sentir isso outra vez."

# game/Scenes/Jamie/JamieTV/jamietv1.rpy:61
translate portuguese jamietv1_5a7eedfa:

    # gnd "Okay, well..."
    gnd "Ok, bem..."

# game/Scenes/Jamie/JamieTV/jamietv1.rpy:62
translate portuguese jamietv1_f08905dc:

    # pc "Yeah, yeah, I'm leaving."
    pc "Sim, sim, vou-me embora."

# game/Scenes/Jamie/JamieTV/jamietv1.rpy:66
translate portuguese jamietv1_17ddf074:

    # "She walks me to the door and we say our goodnights before I walk back over to my house."
    "Ela acompanha-me até à porta e despedimo-nos antes de eu voltar para casa."

# game/Scenes/Jamie/JamieTV/jamietv1.rpy:67
translate portuguese jamietv1_d1f5525f:

    # "If her dad had come in just a minute or two later, this night would have gone much better."
    "Se o pai dela tivesse entrado apenas um ou dois minutos mais tarde, esta noite teria corrido muito melhor."

# game/Scenes/Jamie/JamieTV/jamietv1.rpy:68
translate portuguese jamietv1_a07dd7b4:

    # "Even so, it wasn't too bad."
    "Mesmo assim, não foi assim tão mau."

